  "legacyFile": "blog__2012__02__pendant-project-giveaway.html",
  "imageCount": 11,
  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605243969621-TIORPODZMXP703TOXOCB/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>So delighted to be a part of the <a href=\"http://ohlovelovely.blogspot.com/p/pendant-project.html\">Pendant Project</a>. AesaLina asked if I wanted to be one of the muses for it, and how could I say no? \"The <strong>goal </strong>of my PendantProject is to provide inspiration and encourage others to create and indulge in their own handmade accessories.\" Thanks <a href=\"http://ohlovelovely.blogspot.com/\">AesaLina</a> for including me in this group of creatives. You can see what <a href=\"http://papernstitchblog.com/2012/02/09/diy-idea-stitching-together-a-pendant-necklace-giveaway/\">papernstitch</a> and <a href=\"http://hartandsew.blogspot.com/2012/02/pendant-project-giveaway.html\">hart + sew</a> did with theirs. Next week, Caitlin of <a href=\"http://www.hueandhum.com/\">hue &amp; hum</a> will be revealing hers. Love how unique and lovely everyone's creations are using the same blank \"<a href=\"http://lovelovely.storenvy.com/products/222422-stitchery-wooden-pendant\">canvas</a>\". </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605243986659-16CLG57TDYQT2QAMV5OA/16b-dsc_03141.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>I knew I would be taking a chance by stamping on my pendant and not having it turn out how I envisioned. Decided to simply try stamping it since I could always flip it over to the back if I messed it up. I used the <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=lovestruck&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D36752%2F59151%2DLOVESTRUCK%2DLOVE%2DSTRUCK%2FDetail\">camera from the LoveStruck stamp set</a> and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=versafine&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D23812%2FVersaFine%2DONYX%2DBLACK%2DInk%2FDetail\">Versafine ink</a>. I told myself \"be fearless\", even with your little craft projects.  </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605244011957-USJGDVXG0AAFSRO0F353/16c-dsc_03241.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>And thankfully, it worked. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605244047855-QQ2XEMTLCBHF3PX4BPHT/16d-dsc_0326.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Then I began stitching. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"16e-dsc_0328.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605244084795-2PYOR41YHOWJIZO283V5/16e-dsc_0328.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"16f-dsc_0330.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605244084669-KHR7TM5KIPCCVUE9J5XS/16f-dsc_0330.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"16h-dsc_0334.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605244085660-RW8QQHJAEVZ8ETS7XXBC/16h-dsc_0334.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"16i-dsc_0336.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605244086223-00CTSQP1H9WSD2LVYQ8M/16i-dsc_0336.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16j-dsc_0337.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605244086393-EOF2WXFWCPBOWWUGK2EV/16j-dsc_0337.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16k-dsc_0338.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605244086903-S4MXZEWCTIW3OJ0VIM1O/16k-dsc_0338.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>After adding a jump ring and a chain, I put it on and snapped a photo with my iPhone.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605244135183-FJYQU8JZC2FZXZ704FJ2/16l-photo1.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>I may just have to stock up on some more of <a href=\"http://lovelovely.storenvy.com/products/222422-stitchery-wooden-pendant\">these pendants</a> for gifts. Thanks again <a href=\"http://lovelovely.storenvy.com/\">AesaLina!</a></p><p><strong>*****Now for the really fun part. You all get a chance to win your own pendant. Simply leave a comment telling me something lovely.</strong> Winner will be announced on Monday, February 27. Good luck! </p>"
}